    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Learn about the principles and benefits of yoga with the Productive Fitness Great Yoga Handbook! This handbook features 35 yoga exercises, or asanas that are clearly explained with easy to follow, step by step instructions and descriptive photos. In addition to yoga poses, discover how to use yoga props to achieve difficult or deeper poses. This book is suitable for beginner and experienced yoga students. The book is printed in color and has 64 pages. Make sure to grab this handbook before your next yoga session!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Productive Fitness Exercise Equipment Training Reference Guide Handbooks</h2>\n  <p>Learn about the principles and benefits of different types of exercise with these Productive Fitness Handbooks!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Learn About Principles &amp; Benefits of Fitness</li>\n    <li>Suitable for Beginner &amp; Experienced Athletes</li>\n    <li>Discover How to Use Equipment Safely</li>\n    <li>Suitable for Beginners &amp; Experienced</li>\n    <li>Printed in Color</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/34454/handbook-var_1.jpg\" alt=\"Learn about the principles and benefits of different types of exercise with these Productive Fitness Handbooks\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KH-1-705</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>These handbook feature a variety of exercises that are clearly explained with easy to follow, step by step instructions and descriptive photos.</p>\n  <p>This book is suitable for beginner and experienced athletes.</p>\n  <p>The book is printed in color and has 64 pages. Make sure to grab this handbook before your next session!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
